    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The direction on a macroscale is good as the horror elements are well executed; the direction on a microscale is decent, but pretty standard; the storytelling is a horror rendition of the original Alien movie (following a similiar template after the exposition); they build tension very well as it makes this movie feel like a true Horror movie as opposed to the previous movies"
